				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Pick MMC3 for IRQ's, or MMC1/UNROM and do sprite 0 hit to find where you need to swap the graphics, as MMC4 isn't easy to prototype on as there's only one game that uses it, and you really don't need it's features unless you're making a game like they did. Basically what you do is do a sprite 0 hit or NMI, then switch the graphics to the appropriate bank for the next scanline to use in the status bar or something.</div>

