					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">On MMC1 you can just write the lower or higher graphics page register to the 4KB graphic page you want, swapping it all out. And as for no mapper using another tile from the opposite side, you can't on the background. You have to either switch the table the graphics use, or swap in the other graphics. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> Make sense? <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

